title: SH 121 frontage road construction photos

pageHeader.title: Construction of Frontage Roads
pageHeader.subTitle: July 5, 2004, from Preston Road to Alma Road

text: These photos start at Preston Road and proceed east to Alma Road. Some of these photos show the original two-lane SH 121.

images.caption: At Preston. The land to the left is freeway right-of-way.
At Coit, looking east, showing the original two-lane SH 121.
Just west of Custer, an active project to build the frontage roads was in progress.
At Custer. The freeway main lanes are included in this phase of the project.
East of Custer, the frontage roads are nearly complete.
